3.00	The_Kiss_(opera)	The Kiss (opera)	The Kiss (Czech: ) is an opera in two acts, with music by Bedřich Smetana and text by Eliška Krásnohorská, based on a novel by Karolina Světlá. It received its first performance in Prague on November 7, 1876.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6f/Smetana1854portrait.jpg/220px-Smetana1854portrait.jpg
